==English==

A voice effect of which the normal sounding voice is increased in pitch and often sped-up and squeaky sounding, which resembles the voices of Alvin and the Chipmunks and the Chipettes. It is frequently for comedy in which to speed up the dialog or during a telephone conversation, in which the person on the phone is talking but not visible in the scene.

